    <item>
      <title>日产计划到 2027 年将销量增加 100 万辆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/nissan-new-plan-targets-extra-1-million-car-sales-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日产汽车公司的目标是在三年内将汽车销量增加 100 万辆，这家日本汽车制造商寻求重获市场动力并提高盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/nissan-new-plan-targets-extra-1-million-car-sales-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 06:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
